+#: applications/config/option/PhabricatorPHPMailerConfigOptions.php:48
+msgid "Configure how mail is encoded."
+msgstr ""
+
+#: applications/config/option/PhabricatorPHPMailerConfigOptions.php:51
+msgid ""
+"Mail is normally encoded in `8bit`, which works correctly with most MTAs. However, some MTAs do not work well with this encoding. If you're having trouble with mail being mangled or arriving with too many or too few newlines, you may try adjusting this setting.\n"
+"\n"
+"Supported values are `8bit` (default), `quoted-printable`, `7bit`, `binary` and `base64`.\n"
+"\n"
+"The settings in the table below may work well.\n"
+"\n"
+"| MTA | Setting | Notes\n"
+"|-----|---------|------\n"
+"| SendGrid via SMTP | `quoted-printable` | Double newlines under `8bit`.\n"
+"| All Other MTAs | `8bit` | Default setting."
+msgstr ""
